Package: gamescope
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: SteamOS session compositing window manager
 Gamescope is a micro-compositor from Valve used in SteamOS 3.0.
 It provides a Wayland compositor optimized for gaming with features
 like FSR upscaling, frame limiting, and HDR support.
